## Information on all others can be 
## found at:
##  http://www.movabletype.org/documentation/config

#======== REQUIRED SETTINGS ==========

CGIPath        /cgi-bin/trunk/
StaticWebPath  /trunk-static/
StaticFilePath /opt/local/apache2/cgi-bin/trunk/mt-static

#======== DATABASE SETTINGS ==========

ObjectDriver DBI::mysql
Database trunk
DBUser root
DBHost localhost

#======== MAIL =======================
    
